profile_positions.description:
• produced official English transcripts of interviews undertaken by the Investigations Division. These transcripts were urgently needed by the Office of the Prosecutor in preparation for trials
• coordinated with the Evidence Unit, Digital Department in order to acquire poor audio material enhanced
• liaised with the Investigation Teams in order to obtain more information with regard to a particular investigation or interview;
• reviewed transcriptions carried out by colleague transcribers to ensure accuracy and compliance with the guidelines;
• all documentation is regarded with the highest priority of confidentiality.

• co-ordinated the smooth running of administrative tasks for several engineers;
• processed incoming and outgoing correspondence;
• organized and managed meetings with outside guests;
• arranged travel itineraries.
